SECTION 6 — TROUBLESHOOTING
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

"Connection refused" on port 8000
    → API server is not running. Run: .\start.ps1 api

"Connection refused" on port 5433 / 8080 / 6379
    → Docker containers not running. Run: .\start.ps1 docker

Weaviate shows "unhealthy" in Docker Desktop
    → It sometimes takes 60-90 seconds after start. Wait, then retry.
    → If still unhealthy: docker restart regtech_weaviate

Video stuck in "processing" status
    → Celery worker is not running. Open a new terminal and run: .\start.ps1 worker

Pipeline returns 100/100 COMPLIANT with no findings
    → Check data_quality.ocr_verified in the report response.
    → If false: OCR failed silently — text-based PII was not checked.
    → Also check pipeline_stages.ocr.status in the video status response.
    → Fix options:
       a) EasyOCR active: restart the Celery worker and re-upload with force=true
       b) LLaVA active but slow: check Flower (http://localhost:5555) to see if task
          is still running vs failed
       c) LLaVA timed out: set OLLAMA_OCR_MODEL= in backend/.env to fall back to EasyOCR
    → After fixing: re-upload with force=true and re-run the compliance check.

OCR engine shows wrong model / OLLAMA_OCR_MODEL not being read
    → The Celery worker caches settings at startup.
    → After any change to backend/.env, restart the worker: .\\start.ps1 worker
    → Also ensure you are running start.ps1 from the project ROOT (not from backend/).

Task stuck in Flower / never completes
    → Open http://localhost:5555 → check Active/Reserved tabs for the task.
    → If task shows "RETRY": a transient error occurred. Worker will retry up to 2 times.
    → If task shows "FAILURE": check the traceback in Flower for root cause.
    → Common causes: Weaviate not ready, Redis disconnected, out-of-memory on large video.

"video_id already exists" error on upload
    → Video was already uploaded. Either use a different video or re-process:
    Body = '{"video_path": "...", "force": true}'


